Ok so what is this game about?
- A person is drifting away from a space station
- No one will come and rescue this person
- But they stay on the Radio
- How is this person feeling?
    - This person is angry
        - Why?
            - Becasue they're dying and all their team mates can do is say sorry
            - Because their dying is because of gross negligence from their employers
- How big is this crew?
